org.drip.product.quote
Class Quote

java.lang.Object
  org.drip.analytics.core.Serializer
      org.drip.product.quote.Quote

public class Quote
extends Serializer

This class contains the details corresponding to a product quote. It contains the quote value, quote instant for the different quote sides (bid/ask/mid).
